# 🛠️ Hexify Bug Tracker & Feature Suggestions

Welcome to the official issue tracker for **Hexify**, the all-in-one Discord bot that brings moderation, utility, fun, and security to your server!

Here you can:
- 🐞 Report bugs and errors
- 💡 Suggest new features or improvements
- 🗣️ Ask questions or give feedback
- ✅ Track progress and changelogs

---

## 📌 About Hexify

Hexify is a powerful multi-purpose Discord bot designed to make server management easy while delivering fun features for communities. It includes:
- 🔐 Security systems (Anti-nuke, Anti-raid, Panic Mode, etc.)
- 🎮 Games & fun commands
- ⚙️ Utility tools
- 🎵 Music & entertainment
- 🚨 Logging, auto moderation, and more!

---

## 🧾 How to Report a Bug

1. Go to the [Issues tab](https://github.com/Crxnky509Dev/HexifyBot-Bug-reports/issues).
2. Click **"New Issue"**.
3. Choose **Bug Report**.
4. Fill out the template with clear details (steps to reproduce, expected behavior, actual behavior, screenshots/logs if possible).

> 📝 Be as detailed as possible so we can fix it faster!

---

## 💡 How to Suggest a Feature

1. Click **"New Issue"** in the [Issues tab](https://github.com/Crxnky509Dev/HexifyBot-Bug-reports/issues).
2. Choose **Feature Request**.
3. Describe the idea, how it could benefit users, and any examples.

---

## 📂 Repository Structure

This repository is used only for:
- Submitting and tracking **issues**
- Gathering **community feedback**
- Publishing **changelogs** for Hexify

